<pb ed="T" id="T85.2779.0536a" n="0536a"/>
<lb n="0536a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0536a02"/><head type="no">No. 2779</head>
<lb n="0536a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="0536001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】佛蘭西國民圖書館藏燉煌本, P. 2212, 【甲】佛蘭西國民圖書館藏燉煌本, P.2204</note>佛說楞伽經禪門悉談章<note place="inline">并序</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0536a04"/>
<lb n="0536a05"/><div1 type="other"><p>諸佛子等合掌至心聽。我今欲說大乘楞伽
<lb n="0536a06"/>悉談章。悉談章者。悉談昔大乘在楞伽山。因
<lb n="0536a07"/>得菩提達摩和尚。宋家元年從南<note n="0536002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竹＝竺【甲】</note><app n="0536002"><lem>天竹</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">竺</rdg></app>國。將
<lb n="0536a08"/>楞伽經來至東都。跋陀三藏法師奉諮翻譯。
<lb n="0536a09"/>其經總有五卷合成一部。文字浩<note n="0536003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01990;＝汗【甲】</note><app n="0536003"><lem>&CB01990;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">汗</rdg></app>意義難
<lb n="0536a10"/>知。和<note n="0536004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝尚【甲】</note><app n="0536004"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">尚</rdg></app>慈悲廣濟<note n="0536005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">郡品＝群生【甲】</note><app n="0536005"><lem>郡品</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">群生</rdg></app>。通經問道識攬<note n="0536006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懸＝玄【甲】</note><app n="0536006"><lem>懸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">玄</rdg></app>
<lb n="0536a11"/>宗。窮達本原皆蒙指受。又蒿山會善沙門定
<lb n="0536a12"/>慧翻出悉談章。廣開禪門不妨慧學。不著文
<lb n="0536a13"/>字並合秦音。<note n="0536007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彼＝亦【甲】</note><app n="0536007"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">亦</rdg></app>與鳩摩羅什法師通韻。魯留
<lb n="0536a14"/>盧樓為首。</p>
<lb n="0536a15"/><p><note n="0536008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔頗邏墮頗邏墮〕－【甲】</note><app n="0536008"><lem>頗邏墮頗邏墮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。第一捨緣清淨座。萬事不起
<lb n="0536a16"/>真無我。直進菩提離因果。心心寂滅無殃禍。
<lb n="0536a17"/>念念無念當印可。摩底利摩魯留盧樓頗羅
<lb n="0536a18"/>墮　諸<note n="0536009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＋（弟）【甲】</note><app n="0536009"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">佛弟</rdg></app>子莫嬾墮自勸課。愛河苦海須
<lb n="0536a19"/><note n="0536010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">度＝渡【甲】</note><app n="0536010"><lem>度</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">渡</rdg></app>過。憶食不&CB00068;常被餓。木頭不攢不出火。
<lb n="0536a20"/>耶<note n="0536011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅邏＝囉羅【甲】</note><app n="0536011"><lem>羅邏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">囉羅</rdg></app>端坐。娑訶耶莫臥。</p>
<lb n="0536a21"/><p><note n="0536012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">只＝質【甲】＊</note><note n="0536012" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>只＝質【甲】＊</note><app n="0536012"><lem>只</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">質</rdg></app>領盛只領盛。第二住心常看淨。亦見亦聞
<lb n="0536a22"/>無視聽。生滅兩亡由未證。從師授語方顯定。
<lb n="0536a23"/>見佛法身無二性。性頂領徑魯留盧樓只領
<lb n="0536a24"/>盛　諸佛子莫瞋&CB00126;。三毒忽起無佛性。癡狂
<lb n="0536a25"/>心亂惱賢聖。眼貪色塵耳<note n="0536013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝莫【甲】</note><app n="0536013"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">莫</rdg></app>聽。背&CB00230;天堂向
<lb n="0536a26"/>惡<note n="0536014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徑＝境【甲】</note><app n="0536014"><lem>徑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">境</rdg></app>。盈令<note n="0536015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＝令【甲】</note><app n="0536015"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">令</rdg></app>修定。娑訶耶歸正。</p>
<lb n="0536a27"/><p><note n="0536016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嗄＝復【甲】＊</note><app n="0536016"><lem>嗄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>浪養<app type="＊" source="0536016"><lem>嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>浪養。第三看心須<note n="0536017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">併＝屏【甲】</note><app n="0536017"><lem>併</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">屏</rdg></app>儻。掃&CB00230;垢
<lb n="0536a28"/>穢除災障。即色即空會無想。妄想分別是心
<lb n="0536a29"/>量。體上識體實無謗。謗底<note n="0536018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利謗＝堙i甲】</note><app n="0536018"><lem>利謗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"></rdg></app>魯留盧樓
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2779.0536b" n="0536b"/>
<lb n="0536b01"/><app type="＊" source="0536016"><lem>嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>浪養　諸佛子莫毀謗。一切皆有罪業障。
<lb n="0536b02"/>他家聞聲不相放。三寸舌根作沒向。道長說
<lb n="0536b03"/>短惱心王。心王不了說短長。來生業道受苦
<lb n="0536b04"/>殃。羊良<note n="0536019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">良併當＝浪屏儻【甲】</note><app n="0536019"><lem>良併當</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">浪屏儻</rdg></app>淨掃。堂中頃供養。</p>
<lb n="0536b05"/><p>拂<note n="0536020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">粟質＝栗只【甲】＊</note><app n="0536020"><lem>粟質</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">栗只</rdg></app>拂<app type="＊" source="0536020"><lem>粟質</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">栗只</rdg></app>。第四八識合六七。看心心
<lb n="0536b06"/>本是禪室。法身身法智非一。五眼六通<note n="0536021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光＝廣【甲】</note><app n="0536021"><lem>光</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">廣</rdg></app>慧
<lb n="0536b07"/>日。言下便悟實無密。密底<note n="0536022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＝領【甲】＊</note><app n="0536022"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">領</rdg></app>密魯留盧樓拂
<lb n="0536b08"/><app type="＊" source="0536020"><lem>粟質</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">栗只</rdg></app>　諸佛子莫放逸。無始已來居暗室。生
<lb n="0536b09"/>死流轉不得出。只為愚迷障慧日。逸<note n="0536023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">粟＝票【甲】＊</note><app n="0536023"><lem>粟</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">票</rdg></app>密
<lb n="0536b10"/>逸<app type="＊" source="0536023"><lem>粟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">票</rdg></app>密娑訶<note n="0536024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">直＝真【甲】</note><app n="0536024"><lem>直</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app>實。</p>
<lb n="0536b11"/><p>曉<note n="0536025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">燎＝了【甲】＊</note><app n="0536025"><lem>燎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">了</rdg></app>曜曉<app type="＊" source="0536025"><lem>燎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">了</rdg></app>曜。第五實相門中照。一切名
<lb n="0536b12"/>利妄呼召。如已等息貌非貌。非因非果無嗔
<lb n="0536b13"/>&CB00764;。性上看性妙中妙。要底堶n魯留盧樓曉
<lb n="0536b14"/>撩曜　諸佛子莫瞋&CB00764;。憂悲瞋&CB00764;是障道。於
<lb n="0536b15"/>此<note n="0536026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道門＝門中【甲】</note><app n="0536026"><lem>道門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門中</rdg></app>無瞋&CB00764;。澄心須看內外照。眼中有翳
<lb n="0536b16"/>須磨曜。銅鏡不磨不中照。遙燎料作好。娑訶
<lb n="0536b17"/>耶莫惱。</p>
<lb n="0536b18"/><p><note n="0536027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">按賴＝頞崖【甲】＊</note><app n="0536027"><lem>按賴</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">頞崖</rdg></app>畔按<anchor id="fxT85p0536b07"/>賴畔。第六心<note n="0536028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">離＝堙i甲】</note><app n="0536028"><lem>離</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"></rdg></app>禪門觀。不來不
<lb n="0536b19"/>去無崖畔。覺上看覺除定亂。佛子與眾生同
<lb n="0536b20"/>體段。本<note n="0536029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原＝元【甲】</note><app n="0536029"><lem>原</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">元</rdg></app>清淨磨垢散歎。底<app type="＊" source="0536022"><lem>利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">領</rdg></app>歎魯留盧
<lb n="0536b21"/>樓<app type="＊" source="0536027"><lem>按賴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">頞崖</rdg></app>畔　諸佛子莫楞看。道上大有羅剎
<lb n="0536b22"/>喚。愚人來去常繫絆。染著色塵心僚亂。行住
<lb n="0536b23"/>坐臥無體段。在於眾中漫叫喚。得他勸諫即
<lb n="0536b24"/>橛難。耶羅邏荼灌。娑訶耶鈍漢。</p>
<lb n="0536b25"/><p>普路喻普路喻。第七圓明大慧悟。四門十八
<lb n="0536b26"/>離名數。生滅妙有懸通度。三界大師實難遇。
<lb n="0536b27"/>生死涅槃不合渡。愛河逆上不留住。即心非
<lb n="0536b28"/>心魔自去。去底<app type="＊" source="0536022"><lem>利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">領</rdg></app>去魯留盧樓普路喻　諸
<lb n="0536b29"/>佛子常覺悟。一念淨心無染污。一切魔軍自
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2779.0536c" n="0536c"/>
<lb n="0536c01"/>然去。閭閭屢專注。娑訶耶大悟。</p>
<lb n="0536c02"/><p><app type="＊" source="0536016"><lem>嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>略藥<app type="＊" source="0536016"><lem>嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>略藥。第八禪門絕針酌。不高不
<lb n="0536c03"/>下無樓閣。不出不入無城<note n="0536030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">墎＝廓【甲】＊</note><app n="0536030"><lem>墎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">廓</rdg></app>。是想<note n="0536031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顯＝現【甲】</note><app n="0536031"><lem>顯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">現</rdg></app>聲即
<lb n="0536c04"/>初學。生心動念勿令著。久坐用功作非作。無
<lb n="0536c05"/>樂可樂是常樂。慧燈一照三千<app type="＊" source="0536030"><lem>墎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">廓</rdg></app>。定水常清
<lb n="0536c06"/>八萬鑠。十方諸佛同開覺。覺底<app type="＊" source="0536022"><lem>利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">領</rdg></app>博魯留
<lb n="0536c07"/>盧樓<app type="＊" source="0536016"><lem>嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>略藥　諸佛子自在作莫制約。四維
<lb n="0536c08"/>上下不可度。住寂涅槃同門廓。甚安樂無著。
<lb n="0536c09"/>娑訶耶等覺<note n="0536032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書曰天福陸年辛丑歲十二月十九日淨土寺□比丘僧願宗題迷頭上小自後再堪知燉煌懸公索</note>。</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>